		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Ingested - Ongoing</p><p><strong>[[/save constitution dc16]]{Constitution Save DC 16}</strong></p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> [[/damage 1d6 poison]] and &amp;reference[poisoned].</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> No effect.</p></li><li><p><strong>Repeat Save: </strong>Repeat save every 24 hours. Damage cannot be healed while &amp;reference[poisoned]. Ends after 7 successes.</p></li></ul><section class=\"secret\" id=\"secret-tSBe5DSXqLu6xn8u\"><p><strong>Foundry Note</strong></p><p>The activity includes the save and the <strong>Poisoned and Reduce Max</strong> Active Effect applies the Poisoned condition and can be used for preventing healing as well. Edit the Active Effect on the player, change to the \"Effects\" tab and adjust the \"Effect Value\" to be \"-X\" where X is the total damage they've taken from the poison. This will temporarily reduce their max HP by that value.</p></section>",
